defaultManagement of invasive species is a major investment in 
defaultresource
default for the Trust. Typically our countryside a
defaultnd gardens staff spend up to half 
defaultof their time reducing the impacts of invasive species and plant diseases, most of which are non-native.
default&#xa0;
